data.description: Step into this exquisite townhouse, a true gem built in 2018. With its 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and an open floor plan, this residence leaves nothing to be desired. Nestled on a secluded gated road, this 1,805-square-foot haven offers a generous living and dining area adorned with stunning laminate flooring. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting granite countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, self-closing cabinets, and recessed lighting. Noteworthy additions include a tankless water heater, a highly energy-efficient HVAC system, and a 40-year concrete Spanish tile roof.  Situated in the heart of Mission Hills, this home enjoys a central location that provides effortless access to neighboring areas such as Northridge, San Fernando, Panorama, Van Nuys, and Reseda. Commuting is a breeze, with major freeways (5, 101, 118, 210, and 405) just moments away and convenient public transportation options. Medical facilities, including Providence Holy Cross, Sepulveda VA, and Northridge Hospital, are within close reach, ensuring peace of mind. Let's not forget the proximity to esteemed educational institutions like LA Valley College and CSUN. Opportunities like this don't come around often. Don't miss out on the chance to call this exceptional home yours. Schedule a viewing today, because as the saying goes, "Here Today, Gone Tomorrow".
